definition: Jialing river in Sichuan (a tributary of the Yangtze)

sentences.english: From there you can see where the Changjiang River and the Jialing River meet.
sentences.chinese: 从那里可以看到长江与嘉陵江的交汇处。

sentences.english: In a word, the method has more practicality value on gas exploration & development of Jialingjiang group.
sentences.chinese: 该方法对嘉陵江组的天然气勘探有较大的实用价值。

sentences.english: The water system of the upper reaches of the Jialing River experienced tremendous changes over the historical period .
sentences.chinese: 嘉陵江上游诸水在历史时期发生过重大的水系变迁。

sentences.english: Egongyan Bridge over Jailing River, Chongqing, China, 2008
sentences.chinese: 中国，重庆，嘉陵江上的鹅公岩大桥。

sentences.english: We went on a cruise on the Jia Lin river.
sentences.chinese: 我们坐游船游览了嘉陵江。
